txt.en: 'Cruel and ravenous were the Wargs of Azanulbizar, but only the most fierce were granted the foul honour of bearing Azog and his sons onto the battlefield.'
Many were the Wargs slain during the Battle of Azanulbizar.
'Wargs may be devious beasts, but they cannot outwit a dwarf!'
